{"tid":46080,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"藍潔瑛情緒問題反覆　靠綜援過活","createTime":"2016-12-19T12:04:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-02T08:21:27.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3a3ab8b0db2bbafb71de013aa9835743b15f0dd4","tid":46080,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:04:47.000Z","msg":"+<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i3/pEB2Lm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi3%2FpEB2Lm.png&h=d9803566&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n藍潔瑛多年嚟備受情緒、精神困擾，病情反覆影響工作，導致佢缺乏收入並喺零五年申請破產，早幾年更有傳佢發現子宮生瘤，令佢生活雪上加霜。 <br />\n<br />\n藍潔瑛而家住公屋靠綜援，生活潦倒到行過麥記都只係睇下有無人食淨嘢，無就拎杯水坐低扯枝煙，相信呢一枝煙嘅時間，係佢精神最放鬆嘅時候。 <br />\n<br />\n講起藍潔瑛精神問題嘅起因，外間大致有幾種講法，例如佢曾經自爆喺入行之初被兩個影壇大佬強姦；亦曾有雜誌指佢拍完《大時代》抽離唔多角色，所以情緒大起大落； 但對藍潔瑛精神問題影響最大嘅，應該離不開一個「情」字，特別係喺教會識嘅加籍男友，事關佢本來打算喺零一年同呢個男友去加拿大結婚，可惜到零三年嘅時候，男友怕咗藍潔瑛情緒大起大落，不辭而別。 <br />\n<br />\n蘋果片段：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/F9h4nl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FF9h4nl&d=AyFUqcmf7VqkdZxnFZPfdksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=aff8cea4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/F9h4nl</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唉，一代女神搞成咁真係幾淒涼"},{"pid":"b434ef206574de7c605f4bccee9f9caa38ad295b","tid":46080,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:09:05.000Z","msg":"屌你啲報紙佬又攪鳩人<img src=\"https://ka-sir.xyz/p/HKG_icon/Three_Kingdoms/49.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fka-sir.xyz%2Fp%2FHKG_icon%2FThree_Kingdoms%2F49.gif&h=1dbec01c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e3d9e6490e932b9d2b043b2438803cd032a403b","tid":46080,"uid":3769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:29:16.000Z","msg":"唉 想當年靚絕五台山嘅佢搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c2b42993593acff19edbca39e0649b620ddd6dd","tid":46080,"uid":53122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T12:31:3